	<div class="large-8 columns large-offset-2">
		<h5>A new interaction model</h5>
		<p>I proposed an interaction of dynamically returning pre-defined palettes, ranging from blunt (a few basic options) to granular (many different shades), based on the results set returned to the user.</p>
